    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p>&copy; 2023<a href="https://www.dsnempresas.com.ar/" target="_blank"><span>Felix Menéndez, Soluciones Agropecuarias 2023 by <img src="/assets/images/logo/dsn.png" style="max-width: 33px;" alt="dsn"></span></a><a target="_blank"><span></span></a>
